# Grievance Handling System

A web-based Grievance Handling System developed using Django that allows users to submit complaints, track their status, and receive updates while enabling administrators to manage and resolve grievances efficiently.

## Features

- User Registration & Authentication
- Submit Grievances
- Track Complaint Status
- Department-wise Complaint Management
- Admin Dashboard
- Complaint Resolution Workflow
- User Profile Management
- Status Updates & Notifications

## Tech Stack

### Backend
- Python
- Django

### Frontend
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript


### Database
- SQLite

## Project Structure

```text
grievance_system/
│
├── departments/
├── grievances/
├── users/
├── templates/
├── static/
├── media/
├── grievance_system/
├── manage.py
└── requirements.txt
```

## Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
https://github.com/tusharsingh00/grievance-handling-system.git
```

### Move to Project Directory

```bash
cd grievance-handling-system
```

### Create Virtual Environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
```

### Activate Virtual Environment

Windows:

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Apply Migrations

```bash
python manage.py migrate
```

### Run Development Server

```bash
python manage.py runserver
```

Open:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:8000/
```

